Overnight;;71;;78;;R;;This documentary follows Troy Duffy, a brash, foul-mouthed bartender whose screenplay for an action film called "Boondock Saints" scores him a generous contract to write and direct the film for Harvey Weinstein at Miramax Studios. Duffy's band, the Brood, is also in the midst of signing a contract with Madonna's Maverick Records. Duffy's fiery manner is instrumental to his success, but when the deals go sour, no one seems safe from his explosive temper.;;Documentary;;Mark Brian Smith,Tony Montana;;2004;;NC;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/overnight